{"title":"Scattershot","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Scattershot","type":"markdown","data":"***Obsolete**: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.*\n\n| Scattershot                                 |                                    |\n| :------------------------------------------ | ---------------------------------- |\n| Level                                       | 6                                  |\n| School1                                     | Earth                              |\n| School2                                     |                                    |\n| School3                                     |                                    |\n| Source(s)                                   | - [Iron rod](/Iron_rod \"Iron rod\") |\n| [Casting noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\") |                                    |\n| [Spell noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")   | a bit loud                         |\n\n|   |                                                                                                                     |\n| - | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | Blasts a cone-shaped area in front of the caster with metallic fragments. Its damage is strongly reduced by armour. |\n\n**Scattershot** is a level 6 spell, but as it's only available through an [iron rod](/Iron_rod \"Iron rod\"), [Evocations](/Evocations \"Evocations\") determines its potency. Each casting will noisily launch several weak iron shots, randomly aiming them within a narrow cone in front of you. Higher Evocations skill will result in more individual shots and a wider cone of coverage.\n\n## Strategy\n\n- While the individual projectiles from Scattershot don't deal terribly much damage on their own, you can fire it at point blank range to increase the chance of multiple shots hitting a single target.\n- This spell is very effective at taking down opponents with low [AC](/AC \"AC\"), but as the enemy's defense is applied to each shot, high-AC opponents will drastically reduce the damage dealt.\n\n## History\n\n[0.20](/0.20 \"0.20\") moved scattershot into [wand of scattershot](/Wand_of_scattershot \"Wand of scattershot\").\n\nScattershot was added in [0.16](/0.16 \"0.16\").\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Scattershot - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Scattershot\",\"wgTitle\":\"Scattershot\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":48325,\"wgRevisionId\":48325,\"wgArticleId\":8186,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Obsolete articles\",\"Spells\",\"Level 6 Spells\",\"Attack spells\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Scattershot\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":8186,\"wgRequestId\":\"00d6cfa402dfed93802c26e4\",\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[]});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"ready\",\"user.styles\":\"ready\",\"user\":\"ready