in: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> Scattershot\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Level\n</th>\n<td> 6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>1</sup>\n</th>\n<td> Earth\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>2</sup>\n</th>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>3</sup>\n</th>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Source(s)\n</th>\n<td><div>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Iron_rod\" title=\"Iron rod\">Iron rod</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Casting noise</a>\n</th>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Spell noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> a bit loud\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Blasts a cone-shaped area in front of the caster with metallic fragments. Its damage is strongly reduced by armour.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Scattershot</b> is a level 6 spell, but as it's only available through an <a href=\"/Iron_rod\" title=\"Iron rod\">iron rod</a>, <a href=\"/Evocations\" title=\"Evocations\">Evocations</a> determines its potency. Each casting will noisily launch several weak iron shots, randomly aiming them within a narrow cone in front of you. Higher Evocations skill will result in more individual shots and a wider cone of coverage.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<ul><li>While the individual projectiles from Scattershot don't deal terribly much damage on their own, you can fire it at point blank range to increase the chance of multiple shots hitting a single target.</li>\n<li>This spell is very effective at taking down opponents with low <a href=\"/AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"AC\">AC</a>, but as the enemy's defense is applied to each shot, high-AC opponents will drastically reduce the damage dealt.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/0.20\" title=\"0.20\">0.20</a> moved scattershot into <a href=\"/Wand_of_scattershot\" title=\"Wand of scattershot\">wand of scattershot</a>.\n</p><p>Scattershot was added in <a href=\"/0.16\" title=\"0.16\">0.16</a>.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916225134\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.002 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.032 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.208 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 49/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 220/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1291/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 170/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 3/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  110.132      1 -total\n 66.37%   73.093      1 Template:NISpell\n 25.52%   28.102      1 Template:Obsolete\n  7.54%    8.309      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:8186-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916225134 and revision id 48325\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Scattershot&amp;oldid=48325\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Scattershot&amp;oldid=48325</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/Category:Obsolete_articles\" title=\"Category:Obsolete articles\">Obsolete ar